### ===========================================
### Face Recognition API - Recognition Endpoints
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension
### ===========================================

@baseUrl = http://{{$dotenv API_HOST}}:{{$dotenv API_PORT}}
@apiKey = {{$dotenv API_KEY}}


### ===========================================
### Single Recognition CRUD
### ===========================================

### Save face recognition
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/save
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "person_name": "John Doe",
    "camera_id": "camera_01",
    "confidence_score": 0.95
}

###

### Get all recognition logs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/logs?skip=0&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Get specific log by ID
@logId = YOUR_LOG_ID_HERE
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/logs/{{logId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Filter logs by person/camera
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/filter?person_name=John&camera_id=camera_01&skip=0&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Filter by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/filter?start_date=2024-01-01&end_date=2024-12-31
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Update log
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/logs/{{logId}}
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "person_name": "Updated Name",
    "confidence_score": 0.98
}

###

### Delete log
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/logs/{{logId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### ===========================================
### Batch Recognition
### ===========================================

### Process image for face recognition
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/batch/process
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "image_path": "/media/magesh/NewVolume4/Images/Training/ICC 2011/squad.jpg"
}

###

### Get batch results by ID
@batchId = YOUR_BATCH_ID_HERE
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/batch/{{batchId}}
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### Get all batches
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/batches?skip=0&limit=10
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### ⚠️ Delete ALL batches
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/batches
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}


### ===========================================
### Add Persons to Database
### ===========================================

### Add from default folder (datasets/new_persons/)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/persons/add
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "move_to_backup": true
}

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/batch/process
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "image_path": "/media/magesh/NewVolume4/Images/Training/ICC 2011/squad.jpg"
}

### Add from custom folder
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/persons/add
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "source_path": "/media/magesh/NewVolume4/Images/Training/ICC 2011/Players",
    "move_to_backup": true
}

###

### Get all known persons
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/recognition/persons
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}